<snippet><content><![CDATA[html to custom link formatcustom link format=${1}]]></content>    <description> /1 = convert html code to a custom format0 = Do not convert it.&amp;lt;text&amp;gt; = Convert it if the text is appearing on the website.Example:html to custom link format=1custom link format=[%url% %anchor_text%]This would be used for Wiki engines where a link is encoded in a special way.Also note that ”allow html=1“ has to be set.</description>    <tabTrigger>html to custom link formatcustom link format</tabTrigger></snippet>